<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Mean,_variance,_moments,_an=
d_median"><span id=3D"Mean.2C_variance.2C_moments.2C_and_median"></span>Mea=
n, variance, moments, and median</h3></div>
