l-align: -2.171ex; width:14.082ex; height:5.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \=
operatorname {Var} [X]=3D{\frac {1}{\lambda ^{2}}},}"></span>
so the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_deviation" title=
=3D"Standard deviation">standard deviation</a> is equal to the mean.
</p><p>The <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moment_(mathematics)" t=
