ion></figure>
<p>The <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quantile_function" title=3D=
"Quantile function">quantile function</a> (inverse cumulative distribution =
function) for Exp(<i>=CE=BB</i>) is
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle F^{-1}(p;\lambda )=3D{\frac {-\ln(1-p)}{\lambda }},\qquad 0\leq=
