pan>
</p><p>The <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quartile" title=3D"Quar=
tile">quartiles</a> are therefore:
</p>
<ul><li>first quartile: ln(4/3)/<i>=CE=BB</i></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Median" title=3D"Median">media=
n</a>: ln(2)/<i>=CE=BB</i></li>
<li>third quartile: ln(4)/<i>=CE=BB</i></li></ul>
<p>And as a consequence the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Interq=
uartile_range" title=3D"Interquartile range">interquartile range</a> is ln(=
3)/<i>=CE=BB</i>.
</p>
