splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle p_{\rm {ML}}(x_{n+1}\mid x_{1},\ldots ,x_{n})=3D\left({\frac {1=
}{\overline {x}}}\right)\exp \left(-{\frac {x_{n+1}}{\overline {x}}}\right)=
.}">
