=3DF^{-1}(U)}"></span>
</p><p>has an exponential distribution, where <i>F</i><span style=3D"paddin=
g-left:0.12em;"><sup>=E2=88=921</sup></span> is the <a href=3D"https://en.w=
ikipedia.org/wiki/Quantile_function" title=3D"Quantile function">quantile f=
unction</a>, defined by
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle F^{-1}(p)=3D{\frac {-\ln(1-p)}{\lambda }}.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
