l-align: -2.005ex; width:13.944ex; height:5.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle T=
=3D{\frac {-\ln(U)}{\lambda }}.}"></span>
</p><p>Other methods for generating exponential variates are discussed by K=
nuth<sup id=3D"cite_ref-24" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
